description: Num Rand will give you a random number within a given range. Ask it for a number between two integers, and it'll generate a new random number, inclusive of the two you gave it.
exampleInteractions: Alexa, ask Num Rand for a number between one and ten.
Give me a number between three and twenty.
I would like a number between forty and two.
name: Num Rand
shortDescription: A random number generator for dice rolling or decision making.
